               <msContents>
                  <summary/>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="3ra" to="103va"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2350serata">The Ritual of the Monastic Profession (Śǝrʿāta śimata mǝnkʷǝsǝnnā)</title>
                     <note>Attributed to Jacob of Serug</note>
                     <note>The text of the manuscript is different from manuscripts <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESaqm010">AQM-010</ref> and <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESam012">AM-012</ref>.</note>
                           
                     <colophon xml:id="coloph1">
                        <locus target="#103vb"/>
                        ለዘአጽሐፎ፡ ለዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ <persName role="patron" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14617Zakrestos"><t:roleName xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="function">አቡነ፡</t:roleName>  ወ<t:roleName xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="function">መምህርነ፡</t:roleName> <t:roleName xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="title">አባ፡</t:roleName>  
                           ዘክርስቶስ</persName>። ወለጸሐፊሁ፡ ወልዱ፡ <persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14616MalkeaKrestos">መልክዓ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ </persName>እግዚአብሔር፡ ይጽሐፍ፡ ስሞሙ፡ ውስተ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ሕይወት፤ በኢየሩሳሌም፡
                        ሰማያዊት፡ ዘምስለ፡ ጻድቃን፡ ወሰማዕታት። ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን።<locus target="#104ra"/> ወተፈጸመት፡ ዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ አመ፡ ፲ወ፩፡ ለወርኃ፡ ሰኔ። በዕለተ፡ ዓርብ፡ ዘዘመነ፡ ማቴዎስ፡
                        ወንጌላዊ።<date calendar="diocletian" when="1601" when-custom="253" evidence="internal"> በ፪፻፶ወ፫፡ ዓመተ፡ ምሕረት።</date> በ፫: ጥንትዮን፡ ፳ወ፭፡ አበቅቴ። ፭መጥቅዕ። በመዋዕለ፡ መንግሥቱ፡ ለ<persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10198Yaeqob"><t:roleName xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="title">ንጉሥነ፡</t:roleName>
                           ያዕቆብ፡</persName> ወ<persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS7829Petros"><t:roleName xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="office">ጳጳስነ፡ </t:roleName><t:roleName xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="title">አባ፡</t:roleName> ጴጥሮስ ።</persName> እንዘ፡ ይረድአኒ፡ ጰራቅሊጦስ። ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን። </colophon>
                     
                     <note>According to the colophon, the manuscript was commissioned by <persName role="patron" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14617Zakrestos"><t:roleName xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="title">ʾabbā</t:roleName> Zakrǝstos</persName> and written by the scribe 
                    <persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14616MalkeaKrestos">Malkǝʾa Krǝstos</persName>. It was completed in the year of Matthew, in <date calendar="diocletian" when="1601" when-custom="253" evidence="internal"> 253 year of
                           mercy (= 1601 CE)</date>, during the reign of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10198Yaeqob"><t:roleName xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="title">King</t:roleName> Yāʿqob</persName> (r. <date>1597–1603, 1605–07</date>)
                        and tenure of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS7829Petros"><t:roleName xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="office">Metropolitan</t:roleName> Ṗeṭros</persName> (<date>1599?–1606</date>) . </note>
                                 
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                        <locus from="3ra" to="37vb"/>
                        <title>Prayer upon receiving the habit</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez"><gap reason="omitted"/><hi rend="rubric">ይደሉ፡ ዘይፈቅድ፡ ይኩን፡ መነኮሰ፡ ከመ፡ ይትመሀር፡ ውስ</hi>ንያተ፡ ምንኵስና።
                           <locus from="3ra" to="3rb"/>
                        </incipit> 
                           <explicit type="subscriptio" xml:lang="gez">ተፈጸመ፡ ዝየ፡ ጸሎት፡ ላዕለ፡ ቀሚስ፡ በሰላመ፡ እግዚአብሔር።
                           <locus target="#37vb"/>
                           </explicit>
                     </msItem>
                     
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
                        <locus from="38ra" to="44ra"/>
                        <title>Prayer upon receiving the girdle</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez"><hi rend="rubric">ጸሎት፡ ላዕለ፡ ቅናት።</hi> ወትብል፡ ጸሎተ፡ ላዕለ፡ ዕጣን፡ ወጸሎተ፡ አኰቴት። አምለክ፡ ዘይፂዐን፡ ዲበ፡ ሠረገላ፡ ኪሩቤል።
                           <locus target="#38ra"/>
                        </incipit>
                     </msItem>
                     
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3">
                        <locus from="44ra" to="58rb"/>
                        <title>Prayer upon receiving the skull cap</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez"><hi rend="rubric">ዝንቱ፡ ጸሎት፡ ዘይትነበብ፡ ላዕለ፡ ቆብዕ።</hi> ቅድመ፡ ኵሉ፡ ትጸሊ፡ ጸሎተ፡ ወንጌል፡ ወጸሎተ፡ ሃይማኖት።
                           <locus target="#44ra"/>
                        </incipit>
                        <explicit type="subscriptio" xml:lang="gez"><hi rend="rubric">በዝየ፡ ተፈጸመ፡  ሕገ፡ ጸ</hi>ሎት፡ ላዕለ፡ ቆብዕ፡ በሰላመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ብሑተ፡ ሥልጣን፡ ወልዑለ፡ ልዑላን፡ በስብሐቲሁ።
                           <locus target="#58ra"/>
                        </explicit>
                     </msItem>
                     
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4">
                        <locus from="58rb" to="97va"/>
                        <title>Prayer upon receiving the robe</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez"><hi rend="rubric">ወለእመ፡ ኮነ፡ እኅ፡ ዘይለብስ፡ አስኬማ፡ ትብል፡ <del rend="effaced"/>ፍትሐተ፡ ወጸሎተ፡ ቡራኬ። ወለእመ፡ ኮ</hi>ነ፡ ይለብስ፡ አስኬማ።
                           <locus from="58rb" to="58va"/>
                        </incipit>
                     </msItem>
                     
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5">
                        <locus from="97va" to="103va"/>
                        <title>Concluding rites</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez"><hi rend="rubric">ትእዛዝ፡ ለእለ፡</hi> ይመነኵሱ። ኦእኅ፡ ለምንት፡ መጻእከ፡ እንዘ፡ ትሰግድ፡ ለምሥዋዕ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ወለቅድስት፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን።
                        </incipit>
                     </msItem>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
               
