                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#104rb"/>
                           <desc type="Unclear">Historiographic note on the time of  <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS8550sardaDe"><t:roleName xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="title">King</t:roleName> Śarḍa Dǝngǝl</persName>. </desc>                           
                           <q xml:lang="gez">ወነግሠ፡ <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS8550sardaDe"><t:roleName xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="title">ንጉሥ፡</t:roleName> መለክ፡ ሰገድ፡</persName>  እንዘ፡ ወልደ፡
                              ፲ወ፫፡ ዓመት፡ ወ፯፡ አውራኅ። ወበ፭፡ ዓመት፡ ሞተት፡ <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS8276SablaWa"><t:roleName xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="title">ኢቴ፡</t:roleName> ሰብለ፡ ወንጌል፤</persName> ወበ፲ወ፪፡ ዓመት፡ ሞተ፡
                              <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS5112harbo"><t:roleName xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="title"> አዝማች፡</t:roleName> ሀርቦ</persName>። ወበ፲ወ፬፡ {ዓመት፡} ሞተ፡ <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS7278Muhammad"> መሐመድ፡</persName> ወበ፲ወ፯፡ ዓመት፡ ሞተ፡ <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10343Yeshaq">
                                 <t:roleName xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="title"> አዝማች፡</t:roleName> ይስሐቅ።</persName> ወበ፵ወ፩፡ ዓመት፡ አዕረፈ፡ በምድረ፡ ሻች።</q>
                           
                           <note>The note is written in a hand which seems posterior to the <ref type="hand" corresp="#h1">main hand.</ref> 
                             It mentions <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS8550sardaDe"><t:roleName xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="title">King</t:roleName> Malak Sagad (i.e., Śarḍa Dǝngǝl</persName>, r. <date>1563–97</date>) 
                              as well as <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS8276SablaWa"><t:roleName xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="title">ʾǝtege</t:roleName>Sabla Wangel</persName>, <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS5112harbo"><t:roleName xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="title">ʾazmāč</t:roleName>Ḥarbo</persName>,
                              <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS7278Muhammad">Maḥammad</persName> and<persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10343Yeshaq"><t:roleName xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="title"> ʾazmāč</t:roleName> Yǝsḥaq</persName>.</note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#104v"/>
                           <desc type="Unclear">List of readings from various biblical books;  the note contains indications for readings: a name of a biblical
                              book, often abbreviated, and the beginning of the passage to be read (with numerous contractions). The readings are possibly connected to
                              the ritual of monastic profession.</desc>
                        </item>
                        
                        <item xml:id="e1">
                           <locus target="#1r"/> 
                           <desc>The title <q xml:lang="ti">ናይ፡ ምኵስና፡ መጽሐፋ፡</q> (Tǝgrǝñña) is crudely written, in pen.</desc></item>
                        
                        <item xml:id="e2">
                           <locus target="#3r"/>
                           <desc>The name of the scribe, <persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14616MalkeaKrestos">Malkǝʾa Krǝstos</persName>
                            is written in red in the middle of the bottom margin.</desc></item>
                        
                        <item xml:id="e3">
                           <locus target="#18vb #21rb #23ra #30ra #32vb #34rb #49rb #50va #50va #52ra #55va #58rb #63rb #69vb #77va"/>
                           <desc type="Correction">Omitted letters or words written interlineally in a secondary hand, on these and on other folia.</desc></item>
                        
                        <item xml:id="e4">
                           <locus target="#27ra #28vb"/>
                           <desc type="Correction">Immediate correction indicated by thin lines above and below the word.</desc> 
                           </item>
                        
                        <item xml:id="e5">
                           <locus target="#29va #30ra"/>
                           <desc type="Correction">Corrections written over erasures and interlineally.</desc> 
                          </item>
                        <item xml:id="e6">
                           <locus target="#10r #18va #20r #22r #24rb #25ra #26vb #37vb #38va #43rb #48rb #48va #55ra"/>
                           <desc type="Correction">Erasures.</desc></item>
                        <item xml:id="e7">
                           <locus target="#16vb #28rb #34va #70vb #75ra"/>
                           <desc type="Correction">Erasures marked with two thin lines.</desc></item>
                        <item xml:id="e8">
                           <locus target="#2r #3v"/>

                           <desc type="Unclear">Pen trials (written upside down).</desc></item>
                        <item xml:id="e9">
                           <locus target="#1r #2v"/>
                           <desc type="Unclear">Writing exercises.</desc></item>
                        <item xml:id="e10">
                           <desc type="findingAid">Indications and directives concerning the ritual
                              are written in the upper margin, in ink or in pen, in secondary hands:
                              <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዘቀሚስ፡</foreign> on <locus target="#35v"/>,
                              <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዘቀሚስ፡</foreign> on <locus target="#37vb"/>,
                              <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዘቅናት፡</foreign> on <locus target="#38ra"/>,
                              <foreign xml:lang="gez">እንዘ፡ ታቀንት፡ በል፡ ዘንተ፡</foreign> on <locus target="#43vb"/>,
                              <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዘቆብዕ፡</foreign> on <locus target="#44ra"/>,
                              <foreign xml:lang="gez">እንዘ፡ ትወዲ፡ ቆብዓ፡ በል፡</foreign> on <locus target="#56vb"/>,
                              <foreign xml:lang="gez">አስኬማ፡</foreign> on <locus target="#58va"/>,
                              <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጊዜ፡ ይወዲ፡ አሣዕነ፡</foreign> on <locus target="#73vb"/>,
                              <foreign xml:lang="gez">እንዘ፡ ይኤምኅዎ፡ ይበሉ፡</foreign> on <locus target="#75ra"/>,
                              <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዘሐሜለት፡</foreign> on <locus target="#91vb"/>.</desc>
                        </item>
